ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家港大仲話要搞咩「好心人活肝捐贈名冊」<br />\n可以揀指定捐肝對象<br />\n根本set好晒個台俾人買賣器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你講真架？我無睇新聞！"},{"pid":"22534c7ea848b28cff46f538ef8bcba46e0bac33","tid":213398,"uid":99124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"我想加多一個觀點，係唔係有傳媒關注就可以加快換肝等候時間？一直諗唔明點解有屍肝會比佢換先，如果係比佢插隊，咁原來可以換肝的病人咪死梗？仲有，咁以後要器官捐贈就打鑼打鼓搵傳媒報導咪唔使排隊。<br />\n我真係睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac32c816c8dd398bc81ceb804e77095dcb53f32c","tid":213398,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T12:15:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb1530a9f80498769c1492ac93fec4b2634505b","tid":213398,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8284dda1086ea16d18f502777e3f0a89886d2deb","tid":213398,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598dada6b97fccc9d7befe30d9647843a471dea2","tid":213398,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b53bd695f9933b53a48a03821c2a104dd31b755","tid":213398,"uid":169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:22:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d316916787a743aa516c352a38d3dafe83d4c9c","tid":213398,"uid":78217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捐贈者主動爆出黎，講明「我」個器官想捐俾「A」君，又放埋料俾傳媒，邊個阻到佢，唔通唔俾捐咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係唔俾，<